lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth made three birdies in his last nine holes to get himself within four strokes of the lead after the weather-delayed second round of the Singapore Open on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Makes Mixed Start to Marathon Day at Singapore Open
